creator: LIZ Smart Office GmbH
descriptionHtml:
Enable employees and colleagues to work flexibly and project-related!

LIZ Booker gives you a new free way of working. Use the app to make the most of your office space by creating collaborative work concepts. Modern office concepts increase the motivation and overall productivity of all colleagues in the long run.

As a user of this app, you can:

-Find colleagues from the company & view calendar information.
-Book your workspace, meeting rooms or other spaces
-Synchronize with Google, Office 365 and Microsoft Teams.


*To use the app you need either a full account or access to our demo (request on website).
descriptionShort: Get a transparent overview of the current occupancy in the office.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Fixes a frozen screen on start of the app.
